com.googlecode.sarasvati.load

Class LoadResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.sarasvati.load.LoadResult

  • public class LoadResult
extends Object
    Class to track that a process definition was loaded and the cause of the load. A process definition may be reloaded for one of three reasons.

    1. The process definition is new.
    2. The process definition has changed.
    3. A dependency of the process definition has changed.
    Author:
    Paul Lorenz
